<div class='content-block'>
<h1>Getting involved</h1>
<p>The Xapian developers hang out on the <a href='irc:irc.freenode.net/xapian'>#xapian</a> and <a href='irc:irc.freenode.net/xapian-devel'>#xapian-devel</a> IRC channels on freenode (the latter is for discussing the development <em>of</em> Xapian, rather than questions about using it); the community also has a number of <a href='support/lists'>mailing lists</a> where discussions take place. There's also a <a href='http://trac.xapian.org/wiki/'>wiki</a>, <a href='http://trac.xapian.org/report/1'>bug tracking</a>, and the source code itself is available in our <a href='http://trac.xapian.org/browser/'>Subversion repository</a>. Take them all together, eat something healthy, and dive in - we'll be there to catch you.</p>
